channel.description: Hello, everyone. I'm the owner of Teletubi-Scape. I didn't release it yet, cause there are some bugs i have to fix. It's a PVP-server. Sometimes you can't attack anyone, and you can't die. If someone else hits you, your HP gets stuck at 0. You don't die. If that happens you have to log out and in again. I want help to delete this bug. The base source is: W00tSc4p3 [525]
